4% higher at the time of writing. In this report, I will be reviewing</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1523412783/image_1523412783.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743391-alaska-airlines-stock-surges-15-percent-on-bullish-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 23:03:13"}, {"id": "4743390", "title": "L3Harris Is Likely To Benefit From Increased Defense Spending Amid U.S.-China Tensions", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Leadership\" data-id=\"501650629\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"853px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">olm26250/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>In my recent <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4737287-northrop-grumman-priming-for-offense-when-its-not-needed\">Northrop Grumman Corporation</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NOC\" title=\"Northrop Grumman Corporation\">NOC</a>) analysis I outlined a case for lower defense spending amid geopolitical peace through diplomacy, particularly in Ukraine. However, my ongoing research and feedback from mentors have refined my worldview. L3Harris</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501650629/image_501650629.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743390-l3harris-benefit-from-increased-defense-spending-amid-tensions", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:57:22"}, {"id": "4743389", "title": "Henry Schein: The Kind Of Business I Like But No Margin Of Safety Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Dentist, woman and patient with tools for teeth whitening, oral hygiene and consultation with mask. Healthcare, specialist and person for mouth wellness, dental service and check for gum bacteria\" data-id=\"1939508769\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"810px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Kobus Louw/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>For me, the U.S. stock market is undoubtedly the place to invest. However, it is also arguably overpriced at the moment. Based on Morningstar's analysts' assessment as of December 6, 2024, the U.S. market is 6.9% overvalued.</p> <p>The Shiller</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1939508769/image_1939508769.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743389-henry-schein-the-kind-of-business-i-like-but-no-margin-of-safety-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:52:58"}, {"id": "4743387", "title": "Westrock Coffee: Not Enough Progress And Uncertainty Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Coffee beans\" data-id=\"1397854643\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Henrik Sorensen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2><strong>Introduction</strong></h2> <p>With coffee prices (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KC1:COM\" title=\"Coffee Futures\">KC1:COM</a>) reaching highs, I wanted to take a look at <b>Westrock Coffee Company\u2019s (</b><span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/WEST\" title=\"Westrock Coffee Company\">WEST</a></span><b>)</b> performance and how this affected it overall. Overall, the company\u2019s performance has been lackluster, and we do not</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1397854643/image_1397854643.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743387-westrock-coffee-not-enough-progress-and-uncertainty-ahead", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:42:00"}, {"id": "4743383", "title": "SentinelOne: My Top AI Cybersecurity Stock To Buy Now", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"SentinelOne headquarters in Silicon Valley\" data-id=\"1325784610\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6748px\" height=\"3796px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Sundry Photography</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>We <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741785-zscaler-buy-ze-dip\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741785-zscaler-buy-ze-dip\" target=\"_blank\">recently discussed</a> Zscaler (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZS\" title=\"Zscaler, Inc.\">ZS</a>) after the company reported a solid quarter, but its stock dropped to an attractive buy-in point around $190. Since then, Zscaler's stock has appreciated by about 12% in just several trading sessions. </p> <p>Today, let's discuss another</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1325784610/image_1325784610.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743383-sentinelone-my-top-ai-cybersecurity-stock-to-buy-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:07:35"}, {"id": "4743381", "title": "Thermo Fisher Scientific: Renewed Growth Momentum After The Pandemic", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Thermo Fisher Scientific location. Thermo Fisher offers controlled and sustained release solid oral dosage forms.\" data-id=\"1338072897\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"6000px\" height=\"4000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">jetcityimage</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>In my portfolio, I usually combine high-growth semiconductor stocks with others that have low statistical correlation to the sector. For these diversifying stocks, I look for earnings persistence, minimal dependence on macroeconomic conditions and at least a 10% EPS CAGR.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1338072897/image_1338072897.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743381-thermo-fisher-scientific-renewed-growth-momentum-after-the-pandemic", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:03:06"}, {"id": "4743294", "title": "Anixa Biosciences: Uncertainty In The Pipeline, Uncertainty In Their Financial Outlook", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Elderly woman getting vaccination on arm at home\" data-id=\"1316005364\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Luis Alvarez/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Topline Summary and Update</h2> <p>Anixa Biosciences (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ANIX\" title=\"Anixa Biosciences, Inc.\">ANIX</a></span>) is a cancer-focused biotech working on novel immunotherapy approaches to breast and ovarian cancer. It's been about a year since my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4656945-anixa-biosciences-no-longer-crickets-on-data\">last coverage</a> of them, where</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1316005364/image_1316005364.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743294-anixa-biosciences-uncertainty-in-the-pipeline-and-financial-outlook", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 22:00:00"}, {"id": "4743372", "title": "Kodiak Gas Services: Overvalued With High Leverage", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Storage tank\" data-id=\"2168161508\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andy Andrews/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>Kodiak Gas Services, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/KGS\" title=\"Kodiak Gas Services, Inc.\">KGS</a></span>) is a fine business and a leading provider of contract compression infrastructure in the midstream oil and gas industry. While the company is fine, the stock is pretty overpriced</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2168161508/image_2168161508.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743372-kodiak-gas-services-stock-overvalued-with-high-leverage", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 21:39:55"}, {"id": "4743375", "title": "Wall Street Lunch: McDonald's Review Bombed On UnitedHealthcare Suspect's Arrest", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='McDonald\"s Sign' data-id=\"458737115\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4500px\" height=\"3000px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">TonyBaggett</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div></p> <p>Listen below or on the go on <a href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/wall-street-breakfast/id1358381502\" rel=\"nofollow\">Apple Podcasts</a> and <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/05uLjJxkVgQsRk8LWLCLpx?si=r3_yJgxiQiivJwNQG8WNew&amp;nd=1\" rel=\"nofollow\">Spotify</a>.</p> <p><div class=\"pcast hidden-print\">\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-1\">\n    <img alt=\"\" class=\"pcast__top-img pcast__marketing\" src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/uploads/2018/11/21/podcast_series_header.png\">\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-2\"><iframe src=\"https://widget.spreaker.com/player?episode_id=63256085&amp;theme=light&amp;playlist=false&amp;playlist-continuous=false&amp;chapters-image=true&amp;episode_image_position=right&amp;hide-logo=true&amp;hide-likes=true&amp;hide-comments=true&amp;hide-sharing=true&amp;hide-download=true&amp;color=ff6900\" width=\"100%\" height=\"200px\" frameborder=\"0\" sap-id=\"4\"></iframe></div>\n  <div class=\"pcast__section-3\">\n    <div class=\"pcast__ad-container\"></div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</p> <p>Google took down <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4380720-mcdonalds-review-bombing-google-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-suspect-arrest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">reviews posted</a> after an MCD employee tipped off authorities. (0:16) Citi sees <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4380292-markets-stocks-sp500-citi-target-6500-2025-volatility-investing-projections\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">S&amp;P 6,500</a> for '25. (1:26) Boeing up as <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4381944-boeing-is-said-to-restart-737-max-factory-production-weeks-after-strike-ends\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">737 Max production</a> restarts. (3:22)</p> <p>This is an abridged transcript of the podcast. </p> <p>Our top story so far: McDonald's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MCD\" title=\"McDonald's Corporation\">MCD</a></span>) restaurants in Altoona, Pennsylvania were <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4380720-mcdonalds-review-bombing-google-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-suspect-arrest\">review bombed</a> online after a suspect was arrested in connection with the shooting of a UnitedHealth (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UNH\" title=\"UnitedHealth Group Incorporated\">UNH</a></span>) executive. That prompted Google (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOG\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOG</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/GOOGL\" title=\"Alphabet Inc.\">GOOGL</a>) to remove the negative reviews.</p> <p>UnitedHealthcare CEO Brian Thompson was fatally shot last Wednesday, triggering a nationwide manhunt for the shooter. Luigi Mangione was arrested at a McDonald's in Altoona on Monday after an employee tipped off police. Mangione has been charged with one count of second-degree murder and four other charges.</p> <p>Thompson's murder unleashed social media rage against U.S. health insurers, with many users showing no sympathy for the executive's death and instead slamming companies for denying claims or care.</p> <p>Following Mangione's arrest, negative and one-star ratings were posted for around three McDonald's locations in or around Altoona, complaining about \"snitches.\"</p> <p>A Google spokesperson told Seeking Alpha: \"These reviews violate our policies and have been removed.\" According to its policies, reviews must be based on real experiences with a location.</p> <p>In today\u2019s trading, \u201cLawrence of Arabia\u201d (a film that is essential to see on the big screen) premiered on this day in 1962\u2014and it\u2019s kind of a desert out there as far as the broader market is concerned. The major averages are barely changed.</p> <p>Citi <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4380292-markets-stocks-sp500-citi-target-6500-2025-volatility-investing-projections\">set a 6,500 target</a> for the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" class=\"ticker-link\">SP500</a>) in 2025 and said the ongoing bull market will be met with increased volatility as a second Trump administration converges with supportive market pillars such as AI demand.</p> <p>The 6,500 base-case target implies a +7% rise for the S&amp;P next year.</p> <p>Strategist Scott Chronert said trading in 2025 may bring \u201cmore volatility episodes than has been the case this year,\u201d which was unusually steady with no -10% drawdown for the benchmark.</p> <p>\u201cIn sum, the bull run is set to enter its third year with lofty expectations at its starting point. We believe post-election euphoria reflects confidence in longer-term growth drivers, but our structurally positive view on S&amp;P 500 fundamentals does have a myriad of issues that need to be navigated.\u201d</p> <p>The bull case is 6,900, and the bear case is 5,100.</p> <p>Among active stocks, Oracle (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ORCL\" title=\"Oracle Corporation\">ORCL</a>) is <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4381516-oracle-skids-but-wall-street-comes-to-defense-as-cloud-growth-continues\">slumping</a> after fiscal second-quarter results and guidance that were a bit weaker than expected. But Wall Street continued to praise the stock amid continued growth in the cloud.</p> <p>Piper Sandler analyst Brent Bracelin said, \"While the Oracle Cloud momentum was encouraging, consistent expense discipline coupled with improving margins across cloud applications and infrastructure was equally encouraging.\"</p> <p><a href=\"http://c3.ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">C3.ai</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AI\" title=\"C3.ai, Inc.\">AI</a>) was choppy following <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4381874-c3ai-dips-after-mixed-guidance-despite-q2-beat-analysts-largely-positive\">fiscal second-quarter results</a> that beat estimates and higher outlook.</p> <p>JMP Securities analyst Patrick Walravens maintained his Market Outperform rating and increased the price target to $55 from $40. He said <a href=\"http://c3.ai\" rel=\"nofollow\">C3.ai</a> continues to face a number of risks, including its dependency on Baker Hughes, which has represented about 20% of fiscal 2025 revenue and whose current contract expires in June 2025. But they continue to like the story as the company has now had seven quarters of accelerating revenue growth and offers a range of AI applications for enterprises in fields like manufacturing, defense, government, and oil and gas.</p> <p>And Boeing (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BA\" title=\"The Boeing Company\">BA</a>) is among the top S&amp;P gainers on a report that it <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4381944-boeing-is-said-to-restart-737-max-factory-production-weeks-after-strike-ends\">resumed factory production</a> of its best-selling 737 Max jet.</p> <p>Reuters said work on the plane started on Friday, about a month after a seven-week strike ended. About 33,000 machinists had walked off the job as their union hammered out a new labor contract with Boeing's management.</p> <p>In other news of note, following a sharp negative reaction to comments made on Monday at the UBS Global Media and Communications Conference, T-Mobile CEO Mike Sievert <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4379220-t-mobile-ceo-warns-investors-risks-second-half-q4\">clarified remarks</a> he made that he said were misinterpreted.</p> <p>Sievert said in a press release: \"My comments explaining normal seasonal trends in Q4 were misinterpreted by one media outlet as a warning.\"</p> <p>\"To be clear, our Q4 is trending at least in line with prior expectations, maybe better. We continue to expect to deliver about 3 million postpaid phone net additions for the year, or more. Q3 was a fantastic growth quarter for T-Mobile and our growth momentum continues in Q4.\"</p> <p>Shares are up 2%, having fallen 6% in the previous session.</p> <p>The CEO said on Monday, \u201cIt's been a great quarter so far. The only thing I would caution, and I can just hear myself saying this in prior years as well, is that this quarter's back end loaded. So, while I'm here to tell you it's going great, we're confident in our guidance, investors should be cautious because there's a lot of risk in the back half.\u201d</p> <p>And in the Wall Street Research Corner, for those that remember \u201cThe World According to Garp,\u201d whether the John Irving novel or the Robin Williams film, maybe it\u2019s time to have a portfolio according to GARP.</p> <p>GARP\u2014or growth at a reasonable price\u2014is a stock-picking strategy combining growth and value.</p> <p>To surface these names, we ran our own Seeking Alpha screen for stocks with a Quant Rating of Buy or Strong Buy that have forward revenue growth above 10% and a forward price-earnings-to-growth ratio below 1.4.</p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div><p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/news/4378553-top-names-with-growth-at-a-reasonable-price-according-to-garp\">Stocks on the list</a> include United Air Lines (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/UAL\" title=\"United Airlines Holdings, Inc.\">UAL</a>), Allstate (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALL\" title=\"The Allstate Corporation\">ALL</a>), Taiwan Semi (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSM\" title=\"Taiwan Semiconductor Manufacturing Company Limited\">TSM</a>), Block (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SQ\" title=\"Block, Inc.\">SQ</a>), IMAX (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/IMAX\" title=\"IMAX Corporation\">IMAX</a>), Baker Hughes (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BKR\" title=\"Baker Hughes Company\">BKR</a>) and Okta (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/OKTA\" title=\"Okta, Inc.\">OKTA</a>).</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458737115/image_458737115.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743375-wall-street-lunch-mcdonalds-review-bombed-on-unitedhealthcare-ceo-murder-suspects-arrest", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 21:34:00"}, {"id": "4743368", "title": "Albemarle Stock Is My Top Pick For Next Year And For The Rest Of The Decade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hard rock spodumene ore, commercially important source of lithium. Mine, mining. Held in human hand. Copy space.\" data-id=\"2170513730\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1329px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">BJP7images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Investment thesis:</strong> Lithium prices declined by about 85% from the peak reached 2 years ago. Albemarle's (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ALB\" title=\"Albemarle Corporation\">ALB</a></span>) stock price fell by about 2/3 in parallel with the drop in lithium prices. With both supply and demand growth for</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170513730/image_2170513730.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743368-albemarle-stock-top-pick-for-next-year-and-for-rest-of-the-decade", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 21:28:59"}]}